<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-1024x495.png" alt="18 Looking for" class="wp-image-115218" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-1536x743.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-1440x697.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Weniger Aufwand für die Besucher bedeutet, dass sie die gewünschten Produkte ohne jedes Drama finden können und erhöht ihre Kaufchancen.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="12">12. Produktbewertungen und Rezensionen sind das zweitwichtigste Element (Statista)</h2>



<p>Online-Shopping macht Spaß und ist aufregend, aber es kann manchmal auch überwältigend sein.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Die Käufer müssen oft durch eine Tonne verschiedener Produkte filtern, um das zu finden, was sie suchen, und alle Optionen können sie ein wenig wie gelähmt machen.</p>



<p>Eine der besten Möglichkeiten, das Vertrauen der Shopper zu stärken und die nötigen Einblicke zu gewinnen, ist es, ihnen Zugang zu Produktbewertungen und Bewertungen zu geben.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Tatsächlich ist das für <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/973413/most-important-attributes-online-shopping-shoppers-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">53 Prozent</a> der Menschen die wichtigste Eigenschaft des Online-Einkaufserlebnisses. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="697" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-1024x697.png" alt="19 Top percent" class="wp-image-115222" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-1024x697.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-300x204.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-768x523.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-1536x1046.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-380x259.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-600x409.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-760x518.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-1440x981.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-720x490.png 720w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-220x150.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2-385x262.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-2.png 1636w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Man könnte sogar darauf hinweisen, dass die Verfügbarkeit dieser Informationen einen großen Teil zum Erfolg von Amazon beigetragen hat.</p>



<p>Schließlich machen sie es supereinfach, Bewertungen für die Produkte, die sie verkaufen, zu finden, sowie eingehende Bewertungen von Kunden.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="499" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-1024x499.png" alt="20 customer review" class="wp-image-115226" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-1024x499.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-1440x702.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-740x361.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Und es ist eine gute Idee für alle E-Commerce-Marken, dies ebenfalls anzubieten.</p>



<p>Das ist es, was die Hautpflegefirma <a href="https://www.blissworld.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bliss</a> macht. </p>



<p>Schau dir an, was Käufer für ihr Produkt die &#8222;Bright Idea Moisturizer&#8220; finden können.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="487" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-1024x487.png" alt="21 Bliss" class="wp-image-115228" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-1024x487.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-768x365.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-1536x731.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-600x285.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-1440x685.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-740x352.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2-385x183.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Es gibt Bewertungen.</p>



