<h2><strong>6. Flat Tummy Co: &#8222;Säubere &amp; entblättere oder schneide die Cals&#8220;</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-1024x506.png" alt="" class="wp-image-113026" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-1024x506.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-768x379.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-1536x758.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-760x375.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-1440x711.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image-30.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://flattummyco.com/"></a></p>



<p>Hier ist eine E-Commerce-Marke, die sich auf Produkte zur Gewichtskontrolle für Frauen spezialisiert hat, wie Shakes, Tees und Lutscher, sowie auf Fitnessbekleidung und -matten.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Angesichts der Tatsache, dass die Marke derzeit 1,7 Millionen Instagram-Anhänger hat, hat sie eine großartige Arbeit geleistet, um sich mit ihrem Kernpublikum zu verbinden und eine starke digitale Gemeinschaft aufzubauen.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="557" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1024x557.png" alt="15 $flat Tummy Insta" class="wp-image-112960" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1024x557.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-300x163.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-768x418.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1536x835.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-380x207.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-600x326.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-760x413.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1440x783.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-740x402.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-385x209.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/flattummyco/"></a></p>



<p>Wie ich bereits erwähnt habe, ist ein entscheidender erster Schritt, um auf dieses Niveau zu gelangen, einen E-Commerce-Slogan oder Slogan zu erstellen, der kommuniziert, worum es bei deiner Marke geht.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://flattummyco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Flat Tummy Co</a>. schafft das einwandfrei, indem es &#8222;Cleanse &amp; Debloat or Cut the Cals&#8220; als Slogan verwendet.</p>



<p>Mit nur einer Handvoll Worten wissen die Interessenten, was sie mit dem Kauf der Produkte von Flat Tummy Co erreichen können, was die Aufmerksamkeit ihres Stammpublikums auf sich zieht.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>7. Everlane: &#8222;Moderne Grundlagen. Radikale Transparenz&#8220;.</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="455" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1024x455.png" alt="16 Everlane" class="wp-image-112964" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1024x455.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-768x342.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1536x683.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-760x338.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1440x640.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-740x329.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-385x171.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.everlane.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.everlane.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Everlane</a> ist ein beliebter Online-Bekleidungshändler, der über die Jahre massiv an Zugkraft gewonnen hat. Die Marke hat sich einen großartigen Ruf aufgebaut und nähert sich im Moment einer Million Instagram-Follower.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="596" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1024x596.png" alt="17 Everlane Insta" class="wp-image-112968" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1024x596.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-768x447.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1536x894.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-380x221.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-600x349.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-760x443.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1440x838.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-740x431.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-385x224.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/everlane/"></a></p>



<p>Everlane macht viele Dinge richtig, und sein E-Commerce-Slogan fängt sehr gut ein, worum es ihnen geht &#8211; einfache, minimalistisch-zentrierte Kleidung und Bekleidung anzubieten und gleichzeitig ihre Werte vollständig transparent zu machen.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Um es ganz klar zu sagen: Die Werte des Unternehmens bestehen darin, Kleidung aus nachhaltigen Materialien zu kreieren und sie gleichzeitig auf ethische Weise zu beschaffen.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>8. Freundinnen-Kollektiv: &#8222;Ethisch hergestellte Aktivbekleidung&#8220;.</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="478" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1024x478.png" alt="18 GF Collective" class="wp-image-112972" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1024x478.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1536x717.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-600x280.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-760x355.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1440x672.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-220x103.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-385x180.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.girlfriend.com/"></a></p>



<p>Dies ist eine Marke, die Aktivbekleidung aus 100 Prozent recycelten Materialien herstellt.</p>



<p>Auf ihrer Website findest du eine lustige, spielerische Kopie, auf der steht: &#8222;Girlfriend Collective stellt Activewear aus recycelten Materialien her, weil Müll an dir besser aussieht, als wenn er den Planeten verschmutzt.</p>



<p>Und ihr Slogan passt perfekt zu ihrem einzigartigen <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Value Proposition</a>, da sie nur drei Worte verwendet &#8211; &#8222;Ethisch hergestellte Activewear&#8220;.</p>



<p>So erfahren Interessenten sofort, worum es bei <a href="https://www.girlfriend.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Girlfriend Collective</a> geht, und es zeigt, dass es möglich ist, die Mission, die Werte und die Philosophie deiner Marke in einem ultra-einfachen Slogan zu verdichten.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>9. Primäre Kleidung: &#8222;Brillante Basics für Babys und Kinder&#8220;.</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1024x470.png" alt="19 Primary" class="wp-image-112976" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.primary.com/"></a></p>



<p>Hier ist eine andere Firma, die das Wort &#8222;Basics&#8220; in ihrem Slogan verwendet.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.primary.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Primary Clothing</a> ist eine Marke, die sich darauf konzentriert, &#8222;unerwartet hochwertige Kinderkleidung zu einem Bruchteil des Preises&#8220; anzubieten. Wenn die Käufer den Slogan lesen, wissen sie, dass Primary Clothing sich speziell an Kinder wendet.</p>



<p>Und wenn sie die Worte &#8222;brillante Basics&#8220; verwenden, wissen die Käufer, dass sie ein hohes Qualitätsniveau finden können, was Primary Clothing hilft, sich von ähnlichen Konkurrenten auf dem Markt zu unterscheiden.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Dies verstärken sie auf ihrer Website, wo sie genau erklären, was sie großartig macht.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1024x470.png" alt="20 Primary Rainbow" class="wp-image-112980" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2><strong>10. Sephora: &#8222;Let’s Beauty Together&#8220;</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="476" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1024x476.png" alt="21 Sephora" class="wp-image-112984" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1024x476.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-768x357.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1536x715.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-600x279.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-760x354.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1440x670.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-740x344.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Für meine letzten Beispiele werde ich Marken mit tollen Sprüchen versehen. Wie ich schon sagte, sind Taglines etwas abstrakter als Slogans und konzentrieren sich darauf, ein Bild in den Köpfen der Käufer hervorzurufen.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Letzten Endes geht es bei Taglines hauptsächlich darum, den Käufern zu helfen, Assoziationen zwischen einem bestimmten Satz und dem &#8222;Just Do It&#8220; von Nike herzustellen.</p>



<p>Daher ist es üblich, dass größere, etabliertere Unternehmen Taglines verwenden, weil sie bereits über einen gewissen eingebauten Markenwert verfügen.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Eines der besten Beispiele ist Sephora&#8217;s &#8222;Let&#8217;s Beauty Together&#8220;. Dies lässt die Käufer klar erkennen, dass die Marke Schönheitsprodukte verkauft und ist ein kreativer Weg, um ihre aufgeschlossene Haltung zu vermitteln.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Und mit nur drei Worten ist es kurz, süß und rollt von der Zunge.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>11. TOMS: &#8222;Wir sind im Geschäft, um Leben zu verbessern&#8220;</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1024x498.png" alt="22 TOMS" class="wp-image-112988" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/"></a></p>



<p>TOMS war einer der Begründer des &#8222;Eins-zu-eins&#8220;-Geschäftsmodells, bei dem sie für jedes Paar Schuhe, das gekauft wurde, ein Paar Schuhe an jemanden in Not verschenkten.</p>



<p>Im Laufe der Jahre hat sich die Marke vergrößert und das Modell leicht modifiziert, aber ihre Markenidentität basiert immer noch stark darauf, Menschen auf der ganzen Welt zu helfen und den Fortschritt voranzutreiben.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Der Slogan &#8222;We&#8217;re in business to improve lives&#8220; ist perfekt, um die Werte von TOMS zu artikulieren und zu zeigen, dass positive Veränderungen die treibende Kraft hinter ihrem Unternehmen sind.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Dies sollte ausreichen, um das Interesse vieler Menschen zu wecken und sie auf die TOMS-Website zu lenken. Von dort aus können die Kunden mehr über die Mission von TOMS erfahren und sich ihre Produkte ansehen.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="496" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1024x496.png" alt="23 TOMS CSR" class="wp-image-112992" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1024x496.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1440x698.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/"></a></p>



<p>Und das ist etwas, von dem du eine Seite übernehmen und in deine E-Commerce-Marke implementieren kannst.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>12. Chubbies: &#8222;Das Wochenende ist da&#8220;</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1024x497.png" alt="24 Chubbies" class="wp-image-112996" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/"></a></p>



<p>Schließlich gibt es noch <a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Chubbies</a>, eine der hippsten und humorvollsten Marken für Männerbekleidung, die es gibt.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Zugegebenermaßen ist &#8222;Das Wochenende ist gekommen&#8220; einer der zweideutigeren E-Commerce-Slogans, die es gibt. Und wenn du nicht schon mit Chubbies vertraut wärst, wüsstest du wahrscheinlich nicht, was dich erwartet.</p>



<p>Deshalb ist dies nicht unbedingt der beste Weg, wenn du ein junges Unternehmen bist, das noch versucht, sich eine treue Kundschaft zu sichern.</p>



<p>Aber wenn du bereits ein beachtliches Publikum hast und deine Markenidentität stärken möchtest, kann dieser Weg sicherlich sinnvoll sein.</p>



<p>Im Fall von Chubbies ruft die Verwendung von &#8222;Das Wochenende ist gekommen&#8220; Bilder von Spaß und Aufregung hervor, die sich definitiv mit ihrer Markenidentität decken.</p>



<p>Sieh dir nur einige der funky Produkte an, die sie verkauft, wie zum Beispiel die Badehose für Männer.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="509" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1024x509.png" alt="25 Chubbies Shorts" class="wp-image-113000" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1024x509.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-600x298.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1440x716.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-385x191.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/collections/best-sellers#daily-hot-deals"></a></p>



<p>Und schau dir einige der urkomischen Beiträge auf der Instagram-Seite an.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="636" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1024x636.png" alt="26 Chubbies Insta" class="wp-image-113004" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1024x636.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-768x477.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1536x954.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-760x472.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1440x894.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-740x459.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-385x239.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/chubbies/?hl=en"></a></p>



<p>Ich will damit sagen, dass das Erstellen eines erstaunlichen Slogans ein wenig Finesse und ein gewisses Maß an Kontakt mit einem bestehenden Publikum erfordert.</p>



<p>Aber Chubbies ist der Beweis dafür, dass man es schaffen kann, wenn man die richtige Formel befolgt.&nbsp;</p>


